highlights.text: “blue” by yung kai has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 216 days straight.
MXZI has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “MONTAGEM TOMADA” is the highest at #11.
“Ojos Tristes (with The Marías)” by Selena Gomez, benny blanco, and The Marías is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #2.
“Đến Đây Bên Anh” by Cloud 5 and Dangrangto is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 14 spots at #34.
